<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/cursor') %>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="story-hero">
    <div class="story-hero-img-wrap">
      <img src="/images/sunset.jpg" alt="Braxton Studios x The King's Trust" class="story-hero-img" style="opacity: 0.65;">
      <div class="story-hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-hero-content reveal">
      <span class="story-hero-category">Business</span>
      <h1 class="story-hero-title">The Latest from Braxton Studios: A New Chapter with The King's Trust</h1>
      <span class="story-hero-date">March 10, 2026</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Article -->
  <section class="story-body">
    <div class="story-body-inner reveal">
      <p>Braxton Studios is proud to be in development with the King's Trust. In 2026, we are excited to announce that we are working closely to scale our operations and continue supporting our established clients and partners. This collaboration marks a significant milestone in our journey, providing the foundation needed to expand our reach while maintaining the high standards our partners have come to expect.</p>

      <p>Combining industry-leading creative experience with strategic business backing, our mission is to make high-tier YouTube production and platform growth effortless. This collaboration allows us to shift the landscape of how digital content is produced and distributed for a global audience. By integrating artistic excellence with commercial scalability, we are redefining the expectations for modern content creators and brands alike.</p>

      <p>Starting a creative company often requires balancing artistic vision with strong commercial thinking. Through workshops, mentoring, and advisory support, the Trust helps ensure that Braxton Studios develops a clear business model, sustainable financial planning, and a realistic growth strategy. This professional guidance ensures that our creative output is matched by a robust operational structure, allowing for long-term stability and success.</p>

      <p>From a broader perspective, the success of Braxton Studios also reflects the positive outcomes of the Trust's work in supporting emerging entrepreneurs. As the business grows, it contributes to the local creative economy by collaborating with freelancers, supporting other creatives, and helping businesses develop stronger digital storytelling through video and YouTube. This creates a ripple effect where the initial support provided by the Trust enables a new company to generate further economic and creative opportunities within the community.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/signup') %>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <%- include('partials/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
